When you install it, you might see this error:
>> Can't create admin user:
>> Invalid date_gmt value in CHV\Stat::track
add `date_default_timezone_set('America/Santiago');` to app/settings.php
https://chevereto.com/community/threads/cant-create-admin-user-invalid-date_gmt-value-in-chv-stat-track.8870/
